Text: Changes to Quitam Extranet Site Please ReadEffective immediately please use the following URL to access the Quitam Extranet site hosted by CaseShare quitam Using this URL will redirect you to the secure location of your site The URL you have been using will continue to work but could result in error messages andor additional login boxes being generated when used If you have shortcuts or favorites that contain the old URL please update them accordingly to reflect this change We apologize for any minor inconvenience this may cause As always if you have questions related to this or any other matter involving CaseShare please direct them to by email or call our support desk at between the hours of am pm Mountain Time Thank you Gabe Gabe Luchetta Chief Information Officer CaseShare Systems LLC Glenarm Place Suite Denver CO fax wwwcasesharecom
